data.description: Charming home with updated paint colors & ceramic tile floors throughout features an open floor plan with formal living and dining rooms. Family room has cathedral ceiling, recessed lights, wood-surrounded fireplace and windows with blinds overlooking the backyard. Kitchen touts freshly painted cabinets, 4-burner smooth cook top, double ovens, plenty of storage and refrigerator stays with home. Nearby laundry room with storage and washer/dryer stay as well. Breakfast room has window seat and patio door access to the backyard. Spacious master suite includes private access to covered patio, room for sitting area, walk-in closet and updated master bath with subway tiled shower. Private fenced backyard has covered patio, plenty of yard space and extra parking.
